(R,+,\cdot)
\iota : R\to R : x\mapsto x+1
(R,\oplus,\odot)
x\oplus y := \iota^{-1}(\iota x + \iota y) = (x+1)+(y+1) - 1 = x+y+1
x\odot y := \iota^{-1} (\iota x\cdot \iota y) = (x+1)(y+1)-1 = xy+x+y.
